Contacts - Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy for Contacts
Effective Date: [4th March, 2025]
Welcome to Contacts. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you use our app.
Information We Collect
Device and App Information:
We collect information about your device, such as the Advertisement ID for the purpose of showing relevant ads within the app.
Crash and Usage Data:
We use Firebase Crashlytics and Analytics to collect crash reports and understand app usage trends to improve the app's performance and stability.
Permissions We Require
Contacts Permission:
We request access to read & write your contacts. We use this permission to add, edit, and show contacts only.
Call Permission:
We request permission to make phone calls, which is used for initiating calls through the app.
How We Use Your Information
Advertising:
We use the Advertisement ID to deliver personalized ads in the app. This helps us provide the app for free while maintaining a high-quality user experience.
Analytics and Improvements:
We use Firebase Analytics to analyze app usage, helping us make informed decisions to enhance our app's features.
Crash Reporting:
Firebase Crashlytics helps us diagnose and fix issues to make the app more reliable.
Third-Party Services
We may share information with third-party service providers, such as Firebase, for analytics and crash reporting purposes. These services help us understand how our app is used and ensure it works smoothly.
Advertising
We display ads within the app, which may be personalized based on your usage. Third-party advertising partners may collect information about your device, such as the Advertisement ID, to provide targeted advertising. This is in accordance with applicable privacy guidelines.
Data Security
We take the protection of your data seriously and implement suitable security measures to prevent unauthorized access, alteration, or misuse of your information.
Children's Privacy
The App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children. If you believe that a child has provided us with personal information without parental consent, please contact us, and we will take steps to remove such information.
Your Choices
You can manage your privacy preferences by controlling the permissions granted to the app. You may also reset or limit ad personalization by modifying settings on your device.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the practices of this app, please contact us at
dev.techgallery@gmail.com.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review it periodically for any changes. Any changes will be effective immediately upon being posted in the app.
Thank you for using Phone and trusting us with your data.
